Uses of Package
de.mslab.errors

  • Packages that use de.mslab.errors 
    Package Description
    de.mslab.diffbuilder
    Provides helper classes which are required for biclique creation, such as to construct differences for bit-wise or byte-wise operating ciphers, or to compare differentials for their independency.
  • Classes in de.mslab.errors used by de.mslab.diffbuilder 
    Class and Description
    InvalidArgumentError
    Indicates that a parameter for the maximum hamming weight was invalid, for instance if the maximum hamming weight limit of a value is higher than the number of bits in the value.
